      "id": "maintain_innocence",
      "text": "Keep believing in people",
      "description": "Better to be deceived than to become cynical.",
      "resultText": "You decide that maintaining your faith in humanity is worth the occasional betrayal. Yes, people sometimes lie. Yes, you get taken advantage of. But you refuse to let those experiences harden you. You'd rather be a fool who trusts too much than a cynic who trusts no one. The cost is real, and mounting, but so far you're willing to pay it.",
